# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files, on every platform, including
# Windows checkouts (which default core.autocrlf=true and would otherwise convert
# to CRLF on checkout). build.ts --check does a byte-exact compare between the
# generated seed mirror and the committed source, so checkout line endings must
# match what the generator emits (LF) regardless of the runner OS.
* text=auto eol=lf
